WEBVTT

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:31.216
Ular bizning ovqatimizga qo'nadi,
tishlaydi va zararlantiradi.

00:01:31.240 --> 00:01:33.692
Biz ular bilan bog'liq 
bo'lgan "achchiq omil" ni

00:01:33.716 --> 00:01:37.118
his qilamiz va hasharotlarni
pishirishdan jirkanamiz.

00:01:37.142 --> 00:01:40.441
Deyarli 2000 hasharot turlari 
oziq-ovqatga aylanib,

00:01:40.465 --> 00:01:42.542
dunyo bo'ylab ikki milliard odam uchun

00:01:42.566 --> 00:01:45.334
kundalik ovqatlanishning 
katta qismini tashkil etadi.

00:01:45.358 --> 00:01:48.386
Tropik mamlakatlar hasharotlarni
sevib iste'mol qiluvchilardir,

00:01:48.410 --> 00:01:50.387
chunki madaniy tomondan
bu qabul qilingan.

00:01:50.411 --> 00:01:53.318
Ushbu mintaqalarda tarqalgan turlar
yirik va xilma-xil bo'lib,

00:01:53.342 --> 00:01:55.904
ularni yig'ib olishni
osonlashtiruvchi guruh yoki

00:01:55.928 --> 00:01:57.870
to'da bo'lish 
tendentsiyasiga ega.

00:01:58.124 --> 00:01:59.855
Janubi-Sharqiy Osiyodagi Kambodjani

00:01:59.879 --> 00:02:02.320
olaylik, u yerda ulkan 
tarantulalar yig'iladi,